<% unless @preview %>
  <p>Hi <%= @recipient_name %>,</p>
<% end %>

<% if @custom_body.present? %>
  <%= @custom_body.html_safe %>
<% else %>
  <p>I analyzed recent reviews for <%= @company_name %> and found customers love the <%= @positive_theme_words.first(2).map(&:downcase).to_sentence(two_words_connector: ' and ', last_word_connector: ', and ') %>—solid wins to build on.</p>

  <p>However, feedback on <%= [@complaint_topics.first(2).map { |c| c[:text]&.downcase }, @negative_keywords.first(2).map { |n| n[:name]&.downcase }, @suggestion_topics.first(2).map { |s| s[:text]&.downcase }].flatten.compact.first(2).to_sentence(two_words_connector: ' and ', last_word_connector: ', and ') %> needs your attention, potentially impacting repeats.</p>

  <p>Check out our free report on trends here: <%= link_to "View Full Report for #{@company_name}", report_url(@company.place&.place_actor_run_id || @company.place_id), target: '_blank' %>.</p>

  <p>Tablr converts these into wins—our partners average 22% more revenue by addressing them.</p>

  <p>Open to a 15-minute call to dive in?</p>

  <p>Best,<br/>
  Haider Ali<br/>
  Founder, Tablr<br/>
  <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #666; margin-top: 20px;">
    Don't want to receive these emails? <%= link_to "Unsubscribe", unsubscribe_url(email: @email), style: "color: #666;" %>
  </p>
  </p>
<% end %>